{"tid":150602,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"細佬比肥婆溝左，點算好？","createTime":"2017-03-10T07:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T07:56:23.000Z","uid":45173,"like":21,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"09a5b27211d12dbca965c9bf3929adc79290ea92","tid":150602,"uid":45173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T07:31:41.000Z","msg":"我細佬今年十六歲，佢生得青靚白淨，平時仲好痴我<br />\n我同佢感情好好，佢一路都係一個乖乖仔黎，好文靜、斯文<br />\n係學校d成績都仲keep到top 30，而且仲要係英中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁佢大個仔想拍拖都好正常，我都唔會管住佢<br />\n因爲我讀中學既時候都好中意拍拖，<br />\n但係就係尋日，我先知道我細佬俾個MK肥婆溝撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我怕老竇老母知道會打我細佬或者趕佢出屋企（佢地真係做得出）<br />\n咁做錫住個細佬既阿哥當然唔想咁既事發生，我就無講俾父母知。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知鬧佢都無用，於是我叫佢約埋個條肥西黎屋企，<br />\n個條撚樣都好懶得理咁，屌佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n雖然我細佬都仲好&quot;霖&quot;佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔想我細佬再受任何傷害，只想冷靜咁解決問題，<br />\n好啦，等佢地兩個都坐係個廳度，<br />\n我就問佢地如果扑嘢果陣坐撚斷左我細佬條撚，佢地打算點，當然我都會全力協助<br />\n個MK肥婆話切左佢，而我細佬就話唔用觀音坐蓮...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當我細佬聽到肥婆話要切果陣，突然成個人靜左<br />\n之後企起身拍擡喊曬口大閙個死肥西係人渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我咁大個仔都未見果個細佬咁激動！<br />\n佢仲一野拎起我部手機劈落個死肥婆度，劈到個mon都爆埋，部手機仲痴曬d油脂<br />\n個肥婆見我係度唔敢做d咩，佢眼角紅左好似仲流左少少血，<br />\n於是我叫佢走先，之後再安慰我細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉屌，依家都唔知點收科好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家知唔知邊度換mon平d？萬分感激！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76bd0429b74ab1003a4c500a713b3f84fabcd64d","tid":150602,"uid":86038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T07:33:28.000Z","msg":"屌 原來係二次創作潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d38955299384ace3723074d18ed43545b8c130","tid":150602,"uid":45173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T07:34:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 原來係二次創作潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n改篇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果我細佬比肥婆溝左，jer都咬斷佢"},{"pid":"5bda79fe1bab4e6699894189a66fb19b2d966be0","tid":150602,"uid":86038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T07:34:46.000Z","msg":"仲以為巴打真係比美極搞添"},{"pid":"15a01d3e32cfa409e3714d8a1c68331f64327ef3","tid":150602,"uid":45173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T07:35:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲以為巴打真係比美極搞添</blockquote><br />\n你覺得我無咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">屌</span></span>"},{"pid":"ec4635067e2d3ead160c2fcd5b650876cd0a5189","tid":150602,"uid":89433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T07:36:45.000Z","msg":"識朋友換mon平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50f3ce4bedf8faab4bdd39006b55539bbf4ac5b","tid":150602,"uid":86038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T07:36:48.000Z","msg":"仲以為巴打同我一樣中咗美極既無限月讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkg